GCP Cost Estimator MCP Server
Copyright 2026 zhhuta and contributors

This product includes software developed by zhhuta, Antigravity, and other contributors to the GCP Cost Estimator MCP Server project.

Description:
A deterministic Model Context Protocol (MCP) server that exposes Google Cloud Platform (GCP) cost-estimation capabilities (including HCL/Plan JSON IaC parsing, regional SKU mapping, and comparative calculations) to LLM hosts.

Third-Party Software:
This product uses the following third-party libraries:
- python-hcl2 (MIT License)
- mcp (MIT License)
- pydantic (MIT License)
